text: G. I. Honeymoon is a 1945 American comedy movie directed by Phil Karlson and starring Gale Storm, Peter Cookson, Arline Judge, Frank Jenks, Jerome Cowan. It was distributed by Monogram Pictures and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1946. ==Other websites== * * Category:1945 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Phil Karlson
title: G. I. Honeymoon
